Description:
PLEASE VISIT OUR WEBSITE FOR THE SIZING CHART AND SEND US YOUR PET'S MEASUREMENTS!! We custom make the sokks based on the from found here: http://maggymoosokks.com/?page_id=29
Youtube guide to measuring your dog: https://youtu.be/KU4hMGHTh4Y
The Sokks are great for keeping a dog from directly licking its feet or legs, or chewing bandages.  Whether your dog is OCD about licking or chewing its paw or leg, he has bandages on one or both legs or feet, or if you need to protect your furry friend from making a sore even worse, you can now avoid having to use an e-collar with MaggyMoo Sokks®!
The measurements, plus knowing whether your furry friend’s leg(s) have bandages, will tell us what size and WIDTH Sokks to send. 
All widths are priced the same; the price is determined by the Length – length of the leg from the TIPS of the toes to the armpit.  
The difference between the “Wide” width and the “Regular” width is that the “Wide” Sokk is larger around so that it can fit over a bandage or cast or a more robust leg width.  Likewise, the “Narrow” width is great for dogs with very slender legs compared to their height.  THUS, we need the full set of measurements, as in ________
All Indoor* MaggyMoo Sokks® come with either Green legs (Sokks) or Purple legs (Sokks.)  Both colors have purple Shoulder straps and a Royal Blue Neck strap that can be used if desired. *Indoor – They can of course be worn outside, but they are not waterproof.  The Sokks are made of soft breathable fleece with a non-skid fabric sewn on the outside of the fleece at the foot, so that our furry friends won’t slip on slick floors.  The straps adjust with hook and loop (“Velcro-like”) closures.
Send us your measurements - We custom make them for your dog, with the measurements that you submit to us.  (see measurement chart, and video about how to measure…)  You can expect them to be shipped to you within a week of the time we get your measurements.
All MaggyMoo Sokks®  are proudly made in the USA!
